results.description:
By popular demand we have introduced a fortnightly hackfest!

This is an opportunity for developers at all levels to benefit from the knowledge of other group members. Come along, bring your laptop, and work on your favorite project. When you hit a bump, get an answer!

Come along for a social night of coding, and get to know your local rails community!
results.how_to_find_us: Find us at 156 Victoria St West
results.name: Thursday Hackfest!
